UID:3v1yd_Kp3OJldzYzSzdy-
SUMMARY:Houston TCG Con IX
DTSTAMP:20260701T101450Z
DTSTART:20260703T100000Z
DESCRIPTION:Houston TCG Con IX — Your Favorite TCG Weekend in Texas \nThree
	 days. 100+ vendors. Every game that matters. Houston TCG Con IX is back —
	 and the Texas TCG community keeps showing up stronger every round! \nPoké
	mon. Yu-Gi-Oh!. Magic: The Gathering. One Piece. Lorcana. Riftbound. Drago
	n Ball Super. Digimon. Flesh and Blood. If it’s cardboard worth chasing\, 
	it’s on this floor. \n  \n📅 Date: Friday–Sunday\, July 3–5\, 2026 \n⏰ Time
	: Friday: 3PM – 10PM | Saturday: 10AM – 6PM | Sunday: 10AM – 5PM \n📍 Locat
	ion: 9700 Bissonnet St\, Unit 1500\, Houston\, TX 77036 \n🎟️ FREE Entry + F
	REE Parking \n  \n🔥 Event Highlights 🔥 \n🃏 100+ TCG Vendors — Three Days o
	f Cardboard Shop from 100+ vendors traveling from across Texas and beyond.
	 Find singles\, sealed product\, booster boxes\, graded slabs\, Japanese i
	mports\, and rare inserts across every major title — Pokémon\, MTG\, Yu-Gi
	-Oh!\, One Piece\, Lorcana\, Riftbound\, Dragon Ball Super\, Digimon\, Fle
	sh and Blood\, and more. Come with a wantlist. Leave with something you we
	ren’t expecting. \n  \n🤝 The Trade Floor Is Open Bring your binders\, your
	 bulk\, your trade bait\, and your spec pulls. Houston TCG Con is a trade-
	friendly floor — deals happen naturally here because the people at the tab
	les are collectors first. Three days means three days of opportunities to 
	find the trade that makes your collection. \n  \n💸 Deals Across Every Budg
	et From budget bulk and bargain boxes to high-end slabs and competitive si
	ngles — the floor has range. Whether you’re spec buying\, PC hunting\, or 
	just looking to flip smart\, TCG Con IX has the inventory to make it happe
	n. \n  \n💼 Vendor Space Available Table space is open for TCG and collecti
	bles vendors. Come connect with the Texas TCG community. 👉 Apply here: htt
	ps://forms.gle/KFdA1u3pKRAvNtzJ9 \n  \n🏨 Traveling to Houston? Lock In You
	r Rate We’ve secured a special hotel rate exclusively for TCG Con IX atten
	dees. Book your stay and make it a full weekend. 👉 Book here \n  \nThree d
	ays. One floor. The best TCG weekend in Texas. Houston TCG Con IX — July 3
	–5.\n\nhttps://ccs-houston.com/events/houston-tcg-con-ix/\n\nFrom CCS Hous
	ton
URL:https://ccs-houston.com/events/houston-tcg-con-ix/
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:ccs-houston
CATEGORIES:CCS Houston
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT55H
END:VEVENT
