IMAGE;VALUE=URI;DISPLAY=BADGE;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.houstonfoodban
 k.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/06/FOT-1200x900-1.jpg
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.houstonfoodbank.org/wp-content/upload
 s/2026/06/FOT-1200x900-1.jpg
UID:YIOCkM2Po_Q99EAq6D3Im
SUMMARY:Freedom Over Texas 2026
DTSTAMP:20260701T101450Z
DTSTART:20260704T150000Z
DESCRIPTION:Friday\, July 4\, 3 pm to 10 pmEleanor Tinsley Park on Buffalo 
	Bayou \nThe most anticipated summer fun in the City of Houston\, celebrati
	ng its 39th year\, the annual Freedom Over Texas returns on Saturday\, Jul
	y 4 at Eleanor Tinsley and Sam Houston Parks. From 3 pm – 10 pm\, this ext
	raordinary\, fun-filled celebration highlights the traditions of Independe
	nce Day\, as well as honoring the nation’s 250-year anniversary. As an add
	ed bonus Houston Food Bank will receive a percentage of concessions as a d
	onation (up to $10\,000)\, helping to fill an extraordinary demand in our 
	regional community. \nThe Freedom Stage will be showcasing Los Lonely Boys
	 to kick off the night\, followed by Collective Soul opening for our headl
	iner Keith Urban\, who is sure to entertain music fans through the evening
	. \nFor friends\, families\, and fans in town for soccer\, there is someth
	ing for everyone to enjoy\, including Fútbol Park\, Liberty Park\, the Kid
	s Zone\, Budweiser Zone\, and Dr. Pepper’s Flavor Zone. All of it leads up
	 to a spectacularly choreographed\, Texas-sized fireworks finale. \nFreedo
	m Over Texas draws an average crowd of 35\,000 attendees each year and is 
	broadcast live on ABC KTRK Channel 13 across Houston\, with outreach to te
	levision affiliates statewide to simulcast portions of the event. \nLearn 
	More and Purchase Tickets\n\nhttps://www.houstonfoodbank.org/upcomingevent
	/freedom-over-texas-2026/\n\nFrom Houston Food Bank
URL:https://www.houstonfoodbank.org/upcomingevent/freedom-over-texas-2026/
LOCATION:Eleanor Tinsley Park\, 18-3600 Allen Pkwy\, Houston\, TX\, 77019\,
	 United States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:houston-food-bank
CATEGORIES:Houston Food Bank
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT7H
END:VEVENT
