DTSTAMP:20260701T101450Z
DTSTART:20260707T190000Z
DESCRIPTION:Levy Park brings “Self Care” to a whole new level with Sound He
	aling led by Leala and James. \nA sound bath is a gentle\, nurturing\, and
	 cathartic meditation experience for anyone looking to improve the quality
	 of their life. This act of self-care is beneficial for anyone from beginn
	ers to advanced meditators who are ready to experience a greater sense of 
	peace and well-being. \nThe Levy Park Sound Baths will assist in clearing 
	out that which is blocking the natural vitality while strengthening the co
	nnection and balance between mind\, body\, and soul. A collectively cultiv
	ated safe space offers participants an opportunity to deepen their own jou
	rney of self-love\, healing or transformation. \nWhile relieving stress\, 
	tension and anxiety this sound immersion experience will have you feeling 
	revitalized\, relaxed and rejuvenate. Let the sounds wash away everything 
	that no longer serves you as you set your intentions and manifest your des
	ires! \n* Formerly Astral.WAVZ Sound Therapy\n\nhttps://www.levyparkhousto
	n.org/events/sound-therapy-texas-sound-2/2026-07-07/\n\nFrom Levy Park Hou
	ston
