SUMMARY:NASA Office Hours
DTSTAMP:20260701T101450Z
DTSTART:20260717T100000Z
DESCRIPTION:NASA is bringing its expertise to Houston’s innovation hub! Eve
	ry other Friday\, join us for NASA’s office hours\, designed to bridge the
	 gap between Houston’s innovators\, entrepreneurs\, and startups with NASA
	’s elite experts\, capabilities\, and technology.  \n\nLicense the Future:
	 Discover how to utilize NASA-developed technologies and intellectual prop
	erty for your own projects.\nPartner for Growth: Explore how to grow your 
	own goals and NASA’s mission together by leveraging unique human spaceflig
	ht capabilities and expertise from NASA Johnson Space Center.\nBuild the S
	ector: Help us grow Houston’s commercial space ecosystem.\n\nCome with a v
	ision\, leave with a partnership. \nJust come walk up and say hello\, or s
	ign up in advance here.\n\nhttps://iondistrict.com/event/nasa-office-hours
	-13/\n\nFrom Ion District
URL:https://iondistrict.com/event/nasa-office-hours-13/
