SUMMARY:Houston Methodist Office Hours
DTSTAMP:20260701T101450Z
DTSTART:20260717T103000Z
DESCRIPTION:Join us at the Houston Methodist Tech Hub at Ion on select Frid
	ay mornings for Office Hours to meet with the Center for Innovation team. 
	\nDo you have an idea for an innovative healthcare solution? Do you work o
	n technology in another industry that could be applicable to healthcare? D
