 s/2026/06/ABC-loves-teachers-1200x900-1.jpg
UID:5hI7YtZeoBsiGYFj1WETL
SUMMARY:ABC13 Loves Teachers
DTSTAMP:20260701T101450Z
DTSTART:20260731T060000Z
DESCRIPTION:ABC13 and their community partners are coming together to stuff
	 school buses with school supplies to benefit Houston Food Bank’s School P
	rograms! On the date of the supply drive day\, Channel 13 will broadcast l
	ive from the station to tell the story of the program\, how it impacts ama
	zing teachers and students\, and to encourage people to donate. Channel 13
	 will do interviews with teachers\, schools and students to tell their sto
	ry of how the program helps them and why it is important. These interviews
	 will run in advance of the drive date and also during the event date.\n\n
	https://www.houstonfoodbank.org/upcomingevent/abc13-loves-teachers/\n\nFro
	m Houston Food Bank
URL:https://www.houstonfoodbank.org/upcomingevent/abc13-loves-teachers/
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:houston-food-bank
CATEGORIES:Houston Food Bank
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT12H
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
IMAGE;VALUE=URI;DISPLAY=BADGE;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://iondistrict.com/wp
 -content/uploads/2024/07/CoJ1.jpg
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://iondistrict.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/0
 7/CoJ1.jpg
UID:BBJTh6t4J7JOrbqFxr9Tp
SUMMARY:Ion Networking with Cup of Joey
DTSTAMP:20260701T101450Z
DTSTART:20260731T083000Z
DESCRIPTION:What is the purpose of Cup of Joey? It is to create a connected
	 culture of coffee shop-open networking across our region. Every Friday mo
	rning\, you’ll have the opportunity to meet new and expand your current ne
	tworks\, talk about tech\, inspire innovation\, and create community. \nSo
	\, what is the difference between a cup of joe and a Cup of Joe-Y? It is t
	he WHY. It’s not what you do. It is why you do it! \nAt the Ion\, these ar
	e questions that we want to explore with the tech and innovation community
	. So\, show up\, be friendly\, and make new connections. Know your why\, a
	nd we will get to the future together. \nThe future is only a cup away. \n
	Register Here: https://www.cupofjoey.org/\n\nhttps://iondistrict.com/event
	/ion-networking-with-cup-of-joey-34/2026-07-31/\n\nFrom Ion District
URL:https://iondistrict.com/event/ion-networking-with-cup-of-joey-34/2026-0
	7-31/
LOCATION:Ion – Lobby\, 4201 Main St.\, Houston\, 77002\, United States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:ion-district
CATEGORIES:Ion District
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
