SUMMARY:Mayor's Back 2 School and Health Fair
DTSTAMP:20260701T101450Z
DTSTART:20260801T000000Z
DESCRIPTION:When:August 1\, 2026 \nWhat:The Annual Mayor’s Back 2 School an
	d Health Fair presented by Shell provides 20\,000 Houston area students wi
	th the tools they need to start the school year off right. In addition to 
	distributing 20\,000 backpacks with school supplies\, the event will featu
	re on-site health screenings to include: dental screenings and sealants\, 
	vision screenings\, mental health screenings\, and routine immunizations. 
	The event also connects families to a wide range of health and social serv
	ices offered by community agencies. \nWhere:George R. Brown Convention Cen
	ter\n\nhttps://www.houstonfoodbank.org/upcomingevent/mayors-back-2-school-
	and-health-fair/\n\nFrom Houston Food Bank
URL:https://www.houstonfoodbank.org/upcomingevent/mayors-back-2-school-and-
	health-fair/
LOCATION:George R Brown Convention Center\, 1001 Avenida de las Americas\, 
	Houston\, TX\, 77010\, United States
